-- Lehman may sell entire investment management unit: report
-- 
-- Tue Aug 5, 2008 8:47am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/08/05/us-lehman-idUSBNG33855920080805

 

 (Reuters) - CNBC reports Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc is considering selling its entire investment management business, including private equity and hedge fund stakes, rather than just its Neuberger Berman business, as the bank looks to raise capital. 

